    "Title": "Repel Raiders",
    "Description": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Defend Location\nAPPROVAL CODE = ~mission(ApprovalCode)\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nThere\u2019s a serious problem brewing for one of our clients at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. They\u2019ve been warned that a highly skilled outlaw crew has their sights set on overrunning and occupying that location. We\u2019ve been hired to make sure that doesn\u2019t happen. \n\nNeed a contractor to deploy to the location immediately. Based on the intel provided by the client, this won\u2019t be a walk in the park. We strongly advise you to bring allies and plenty of supplies to help ward of the impending attack.   \n\nPayment will be issued upon successful completion of contract.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
